item.title: TikTok, the new kid on the block
item.description: We’re creeping into the world of TikTok, the app that is everyone’s guilty pleasure. It’s getting a bad rep because of all the 12-year-olds, but man once you’re on it you’re on it, and you’re not getting off.

item.title: After months of blacklisting .. Huawei launches superior technology for the fifth generation
item.description: BEIJING (Reuters) – China’s Huawei on Wednesday launched a new generation of mobile phone antennas for its 5G network and expects an acceleration in network upgrades led by the three operators in its huge Chinese market.
